### ✅ Actualizar un usuario de armario
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/wardrobe-users/update/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "newUser1"
}

### ✅ Eliminar un usuario de armario
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/wardrobe-users/remove/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
